4d68d347","tid":330940,"uid":34622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T02:28:20.000Z","msg":"同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f339ba0f4404ec275093ccb66b94b4b4e1b0bd2f","tid":330940,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T03:02:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不過個故仔唔用阿童木個名都可以<br />\n除左個彩蛋唔關事</blockquote><br />\n天馬同茶水咪係發明阿童木個兩個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b47e0a29eaade483fd34047a285cb967cdcf5c0d","tid":330940,"uid":7307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T03:22:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>不過個故仔唔用阿童木個名都可以<br />\n除左個彩蛋唔關事</blockquote><br />\n天馬同茶水咪係發明阿童木個兩個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我意思係個故事唔用 天馬同茶水依兩個名一樣成立<br />\n故事上表現唔同阿童木有咩關係（除左角色名）"},{"pid":"ab8eea0c07e5693ecc1b46714e6eb586be835a06","tid":330940,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T12:04:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45b450e3b9067559e240b5571b1e0315014e7f12","tid":330940,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T12:06:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>不過個故仔唔用阿童木個名都可以<br />\n除左個彩蛋唔關事</blockquote><br />\n天馬同茶水咪係發明阿童木個兩個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我意思係個故事唔用 天馬同茶水依兩個名一樣成立<br />\n故事上表現唔同阿童木有咩關係（除左角色名）</blockquote><br />\n原作漫畫黎<br />\n可能後面會提多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0696fd65a84663acb86bca172e88fa3952525bd2","tid":330940,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T12:19:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>不過個故仔唔用阿童木個名都可以<br />\n除左個彩蛋唔關事</blockquote><br />\n天馬同茶水咪係發明阿童木個兩個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我意思係個故事唔用 <span style=\"color: red;\">天馬同茶水</span>依兩個名一樣成立<br />\n故事上表現唔同阿童木有咩關係（除左角色名）</blockquote><br />\n印象中，A107正正就係阿童木既原型<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nA106係人工意識既起點，掌握「自我」既慨念<br />\n天馬創造左阿童木，<br />\n因為天馬個仔死左，阿童木既外型完全係天馬個仔既樣<br />\n不過天馬最後發現機械人始終只係機械人，<br />\n唔會長高唔會長大，<br />\n所有既感情只係人造既，本質只係死物<br />\n所以將阿童木廢棄，而茶水就執左阿童木黎養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n至於你話完全係兩個故事，我唔同意<br />\n因為「阿童木起源」只係前傳，<br />\n解釋左A10系列起源，同馬爾斯機械人既首次接觸（之後第n代亦係阿童木死對頭)<br />\n亦同時詳細解釋左天馬同茶水日後係本傳亦敵亦友既關係，仲有價值觀衝突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而且所有設定基本同本傳無咩抵觸<br />\n本人認為好精彩，<br />\n不論作為一篇重新演譯舊作，定一篇獨立動畫，<br />\n都係佳作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11e9246b90f3e79039099c87fd82b859888a060a","tid":330940,"uid":34622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T12:21:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>不過個故仔唔用阿童木個名都可以<br />\n除左個彩蛋唔關事</blockquote><br />\n天馬同茶水咪係發明阿童木個兩個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我意思係個故事唔用 <span style=\"color: red;\">天馬同茶水</span>依兩個名一樣成立<br />\n故事上表現唔同阿童木有咩關係（除左角色名）</blockquote><br />\n印象中，A107正正就係阿童木既原型<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nA106係人工意識既起點，掌握「自我」既慨念<br />\n天馬創造左阿童木，<br />\n因為天馬個仔死左，阿童木既外型完全係天馬個仔既樣<br />\n不過天馬最後發現機械人始終只係機械人，<br />\n唔會長高唔會長大，<br />\n所有既感情只係人造既，本質只係死物<br />\n所以將阿童木廢棄，而茶水就執左阿童木黎養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n至於你話完全係兩個故事，我唔同意<br />\n因為「阿童木起源」只係前傳，<br />\n解釋左A10系列起源，同馬爾斯機械人既首次接觸（之後第n代亦係阿童木死對頭)<br />\n亦同時詳細解釋左天馬同茶水日後係本傳亦敵亦友既關係，仲有價值觀衝突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而且所有設定基本同本傳無咩抵觸<br />\n本人認為好精彩，<br />\n不論作為一篇重新演譯舊作，定一篇獨立動畫，<br />\n都係佳作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n依家佢地咁gay, 好難想怪之後點亦敵亦友<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}